---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | iptv uk" description="Terms of service for iptv uk.">
  <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary tracking-tight">iptv uk</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-grow bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 prose text-gray-700">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-secondary mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
      
      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using the iptv uk service, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you disagree with any part of the terms, you do not have permission to access the service.</p>
      
      <h2>2. Service Usage</h2>
      <p>Our service provides access to IPTV streams. You agree not to share your account credentials or attempt to restream our content.</p>

      <h2>3. Refunds</h2>
      <p>We offer a 7-day money-back guarantee if you are unsatisfied with the stability or quality of our streams.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
